lead_paragraph: Edmond Sumner ditched the tape on his injured finger and played his best all-around game, a good sign for No. 17 Xavier as it enters Big East play.

headline.print_headline: Sumner Has 14, No. 17 Xavier Beats Eastern Washington 85-56
